cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper focuses on face recognition using deep learning techniques, specifically convolutional neural networks (CNNs), which are commonly used in computer vision and image processing (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the training process and the need for clean and correctly labelled training data, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The evaluation of facial landmarking and pose correction algorithms also falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
